1) Shoulder Press - 4 x 8-10
2) Seated Front Raises - 3 x 10-12
3) Upright Row (Wide) - 3 x 10-12
4) Close Grip Press - 3/4 x 8-10
5) Lat Raises - 3 x 10-12
6) Seated Shrugs - 4 x 8-10
7) Single Arm Reverse Fly - 3 x 10-12 Each Arm
(90sec Rest Between Sets & 2min Between Exercises, DON’T BE A BITCH!)
